# ── Model Weights & Checkpoints ──────────────────────────
# Keep model/ directory tracked, but ignore large raw checkpoints.
# Only the final exported weight (≤10 MB) should be committed.
checkpoints/
runs/
wandb/
lightning_logs/
*.pth
*.pt
*.ckpt
*.pkl
*.bin
# Exception: allow the final submission weight
!model/*.pth
!model/*.pt
!model/*.onnx

